						               													<description>With this Errata pack you will be able to update the content of all V2 products related to the Heroes of Normandie &amp;ndash; Big Red One Edition Kickstarter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     The update sheet clears up a few rule points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     The punchboard corrects a few counters (7) and brings the American army an M16 MGMC, an M8 Scott, and a Heroic Pin up. The German army also gets a heroic Pin up with this corrective punchboard.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     The corrective sticker sheets will allow you to update your booklets (Core Box BRO rules booklet &amp;amp; scenario booklet + Battlepack#1 Bloody Omaha booklet + Solo mode rules &amp;amp; scenarios booklet). Indeed, with these stickers, there is no need to reprint the latest version of the rules at home. We avoid waste and improve our products so that you get the best gaming experience. Our game books have so many elements, rules, and other things to consider that even with two fantastic proofreading teams, one for each language (3&amp;times;2 people), a few mistakes still slip through.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
